<title>ṣʿb ʿlyk</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 ạlqrạr- (ṣʿb ʿlyk ạ̉yhạ ạlạ̹nsạn ạ̉n tḥyạ dwn nʿmẗ ạlạ̹ymạn)2
 1- bḥb ʿjyb lkl ạlkẖṭạh ạ̉tạnạ wsyṭ lʿhd jdyd
 bạ̉dẖky̱ ạldmạʾ ạ̉ftdạnạ ạlmsyḥ bṣmt wḥb zṣạr ạldẖbyḥ
 lyʿṭy ḥyạẗ lkl ạ̉tẖym fynjw wyḥẓy̱ bdạr ạlnʿym
 2- ḥsạb ʿqạb fy ywm qryb yạ mn dst ạ̹bn ạlạ̹lh ạlḥbyb
 yạmn qd ḥsbt dmạʾ ạlmsyḥ lạtkfy lạ tsẖfy ạ̉ḥtqrt ạlṣlyb
 sybqy̱ ạlṣlyb lynjw ạlbʿyd wạ̉nt stbqy̱ fy mwt ạ̉kyd
 3- ʿdẖạb wnạr ʿdẖạb ʿdẖạb yạ mn qdjmḥt bfkr ạlfsạd
 fy sẖr wkẖbtẖ ḍllt ạlṭryq bjhl nʿmt bmạ lạ ylyq
 syạ̉tyk ywmạ aⁿtnạl ạljzạʾ yạ mn qd rfḍt ạ̹lh ạlsmạʾ</lyrics>
</song>